  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the efficacy and safety of bilateral deep brain
      stimulation of the internal globus pallidus for treating idiopathic generalized or severe
      segmental dystonia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
